{"tid":395492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台華航兩維修員遭艙門彈飛重傷","createTime":"2017-09-10T23:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T23:45:35.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"118bbddfa4a987cb723c79658c785be715325e23","tid":395492,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://apps.exmoo.com/exmoo/upload/article/image/e8e2e1e9-fe01-448a-b5c7-fd5c0dea9d90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapps.exmoo.com%2Fexmoo%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Fimage%2Fe8e2e1e9-fe01-448a-b5c7-fd5c0dea9d90.jpg&h=e2c9deb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名中華航空公司維修員，昨日（9日）7時許，在桃園機場華航停機棚內，維修飛機時，疑因操作不當而發生意外，導致兩人開門時被艙門推倒摔落地面，導致二人重傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩人當時登上工作車時，擔心艙內氣溫太高，請其他同事打開艙門，卻沒提醒同事內外有氣壓差，令10多噸的艙門突然猛烈打開，將二人撞飛，並從約三、四層樓高的工作車上墮地。醫護人員到達現場時，地面染有血跡，其中一人頭骨破裂，已由機場消防隊送醫；另一人意識清醒，但嚴重骨折，右眼角撕裂傷、右手穿刺傷、全身多處擦傷，亦已送院醫治。<br />\n<br />\n華航對事件回應表示，目前已啟動調查程序，確認意外發生原因，並向勞動部北區職安中心進行職業災害通報。<br />\n<img src=\"http://apps.exmoo.com/exmoo/upload/article/image/67c5acaf-f65f-417e-b83b-e31048db7068.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapps.exmoo.com%2Fexmoo%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Fimage%2F67c5acaf-f65f-417e-b83b-e31048db7068.jpg&h=ae8983af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://apps.exmoo.com/exmoo/upload/article/image/eccbb613-21d5-4c2c-9f76-7fc498d5ae7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapps.exmoo.com%2Fexmoo%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Fimage%2Feccbb613-21d5-4c2c-9f76-7fc498d5ae7d.jpg&h=aa7eba59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.exmoo.com/article/40076.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F40076.html&d=3xCMysoeWQKAvrXOxL%2FWidr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8ffe91e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.exmoo.com/article/40076.html</a>"},{"pid":"e712d515576c0712374c94d008d2d0e6b6749939","tid":395492,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:45:11.000Z","msg":"諗起大陸海軍果單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 海水壓力太大倒灌 兩隻蝗兵俾個艙門爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後支那解放軍話兩人無大礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8328dc27ec0e53260cbf6bee6ca16f939069accf","tid":395492,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:45:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人有gif?"}]}